Description: kde color picker
 contains a color chooser for kde
 .
 This metapackage includes a collection of graphics applications
 provided with the official release of KDE.

Package: kruler
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: a screen ruler and color measurement tool for KDE
 Kruler is a screen ruler (using pixels) and color measurement tool for KDE.
 .
 This package is part of KDE, as a component of the KDE graphics module.
 See the 'kde' and 'kdegraphics' packages for more information.

Package: kolourpaint4
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: a simple paint program for KDE
 KolourPaint is a very simple paint program for KDE. It aims to be
 conceptually simple to understand; providing a level of functionality
 targeted towards the average user. It's designed for daily tasks like:
 .
  * Painting - drawing diagrams and "finger painting"
  * Image Manipulation - editing screenshots and photos; applying effects
  * Icon Editing - drawing clipart and logos with transparency
 .
 This package is part of KDE, as a component of the KDE graphics module.
 See the 'kde' and 'kdegraphics' packages for more information.

Package: kscan
