Package: okular
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: document viewer for KDE
 okular allows you to view documents in many formats
 * postscript
 * pdf
 * OpenDocument format (odf)
 * comic books
 * dvi files
  - and several others
 and with additionally backends installed also
 * chm files
 * tiff files
 * djvu files
 .
 This package is part of KDE, as a component of the KDE graphics module.
 See the 'kde' and 'kdegraphics' packages for more information.

Package: libokularcore1
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: core library for okular, a kde document viewer
 .
 This package is part of KDE, as a component of the KDE graphics module.
 See the 'kde' and 'kdegraphics' packages for more information.

Package: okular-dev
Architecture: any
Depends: libokularcore1 (= ${source:Version})
Description: development files for okular
 development headers used when writing backends for okular.
 .
 This package is part of KDE, as a component of the KDE graphics module.
 See the 'kde' and 'kdegraphics' packages for more information.

Package: okular-extra-backends
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: extra backends for okular
